						<summary>

						

						<p>Slab set up near the police station, being removed from Jaṅgla-Pōtēnār.</p>						

						<p>This fragmentary inscription may palaeographically be assigned to c. 12th Century A.D. It seems to record some grant of land. Other details are not known.</p>						

